    "title": "Event",
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "overview": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "startDate": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "endDate": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "creatorId": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false
        }
    },
    "required": [
        "eventId"
    ],
    "patternProperties": {
        "eventId": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false
        }
    }
}
